---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | FirstLayer Digital" description="Maryland-based engineering firm specializing in operational infrastructure, internal tools, data dashboards, and private cloud solutions. Custom business infrastructure built for growth.">
	<main class="relative overflow-hidden">
		<!-- Background gradient layers for depth -->
		<div class="fixed inset-0 -z-10">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-cyan-50/20 to-slate-50"></div>
			<div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-cyan-200/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
			<div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-200/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="max-w-6xl 2xl:max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
			<!-- Floating decorative elements -->
			<div class="absolute -left-20 top-32 hidden xl:block 2xl:left-0 w-40 h-40 2xl:w-48 2xl:h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/15 to-transparent rounded-3xl blur-xl rotate-12"></div>
			<div class="absolute -right-20 top-48 hidden xl:block 2xl:right-0 w-36 h-36 2xl:w-44 2xl:h-44 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/15 to-transparent rounded-2xl blur-xl -rotate-12"></div>
			
			<div class="relative text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16 md:mb-20">
				<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl 2xl:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-tight">
					Versatile Solutions, <span class="text-cyan-600 relative">
						<span class="relative z-10">Engineered</span>
						<span class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400/8 to-cyan-600/8 blur-lg -z-0"></span>
					</span> for Growth
				</h1>
				<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-2xl 2xl:text-3xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl 2xl:max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed px-2">
					We bridge the gap between custom engineering and operational infrastructure. From data dashboards and private cloud deployments to high-speed websites and e-commerce platforms, we build the tools your business needs.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-10 md:gap-12 items-start mb-12 sm:mb-16 md:mb-20">
				<div class="relative">
					<div class="bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border border-white/20">
						<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50/30 via-transparent to-blue-50/20 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl -z-10"></div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-3xl 2xl:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">The Engineer's Advantage</h2>
						<p class="text-slate-700 mb-4 sm:mb-5 leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-lg 2xl:text-xl">
							Many agencies are limited to one tool. At FirstLayer Digital, we take a Computer Science approach to the entire web ecosystem. We don't just drag and drop; we configure, optimize, and engineer solutions that fit <em class="text-slate-900">your</em> specific business needs.
						</p>
						<p class="text-slate-700 mb-4 sm:mb-5 leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-lg 2xl:text-xl">
							We specialize in <strong class="text-slate-900">Operational Infrastructure</strong> including <strong class="text-slate-900">Data Dashboards</strong> (Streamlit), <strong class="text-slate-900">Private Cloud</strong> solutions (Proxmox, Nextcloud), and <strong class="text-slate-900">Internal Tools</strong> development. We also build complex <strong class="text-slate-900">E-commerce</strong> environments, configure <strong class="text-slate-900">Inventory Management</strong> systems, and create <strong class="text-slate-900">Professional Portfolios</strong> that stand out.
						</p>
						<p class="text-slate-700 mb-4 sm:mb-5 leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-lg 2xl:text-xl">
							Photo, video, and text editing services are standard services we perform as part of most website development projects, ensuring your content looks polished and professional.
						</p>
						<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-semibold text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-lg 2xl:text-xl">
							Already have a site? We can optimize it. Need something new? We can build it. We bring technical precision to every platform we touch.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="relative">
					<div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200/60">
						<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50/50 to-cyan-50/30 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl -z-10"></div>
						<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-xl 2xl:text-2xl">Platforms We Master</h3>
						<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:gap-4 text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-sm lg:text-sm 2xl:text-base font-medium mb-6 sm:mb-8">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500 rounded-full"></div>
								<span>WordPress</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
								<span>Shopify</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></div>
								<span>Astro / Custom</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full"></div>
								<span>Wix</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-slate-500 rounded-full"></div>
								<span>Squarespace</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full"></div>
								<span>Weebly</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-gray-800 rounded-full"></div>
								<span>Square</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
								<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full"></div>
								<span>Others on Request</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 border-t border-slate-200/60 pt-4 sm:pt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-xl 2xl:text-2xl">Core Services</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3 text-slate-700 mb-6">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md">✓</div>
								<span class="font-medium">E-commerce & Inventory Setup</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md">✓</div>
								<span class="font-medium">Professional Portfolios</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md">✓</div>
								<span class="font-medium">Business Site Migrations</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 shadow-md">✓</div>
								<span class="font-medium">Photo, Video & Text Editing</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						
						<div class="border-t border-slate-200/60 pt-4 sm:pt-6">
							<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-xl 2xl:text-2xl">Follow Us</h3>
							<a href="https://www.instagram.com/firstlayerdigital/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-700 hover:text-cyan-600 transition-colors group">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-label="Instagram">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.315 2c2.43 0 2.784.013 3.808.06 1.064.049 1.791.218 2.427.465a4.902 4.902 0 011.772 1.153 4.902 4.902 0 011.153 1.772c.247.636.416 1.363.465 2.427.048 1.067.06 1.407.06 4.123v.08c0 2.643-.012 2.987-.06 4.043-.049 1.064-.218 1.791-.465 2.427a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153 1.772 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772 1.153c-.636.247-1.363.416-2.427.465-1.067.048-1.407.06-4.123.06h-.08c-2.643 0-2.987-.012-4.043-.06-1.064-.049-1.791-.218-2.427-.465a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772-1.153 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153-1.772c-.247-.636-.416-1.363-.465-2.427-.047-1.024-.06-1.379-.06-3.808v-.63c0-2.43.013-2.784.06-3.808.049-1.064.218-1.791.465-2.427a4.902 4.902 0 011.153-1.772A4.902 4.902 0 015.45 2.525c.636-.247 1.363-.416 2.427-.465C8.901 2.013 9.256 2 11.685 2h.63zm-.081 1.802h-.468c-2.456 0-2.784.011-3.807.058-.975.045-1.504.207-1.857.344-.467.182-.8.398-1.15.748-.35.35-.566.683-.748 1.15-.137.353-.3.882-.344 1.857-.047 1.023-.058 1.351-.058 3.807v.468c0 2.456.011 2.784.058 3.807.045.975.207 1.504.344 1.857.182.466.399.8.748 1.15.35.35.683.566 1.15.748.353.137.882.3 1.857.344 1.054.048 1.37.058 4.041.058h.08c2.597 0 2.917-.01 3.96-.058.976-.045 1.505-.207 1.858-.344.466-.182.8-.398 1.15-.748.35-.35.566-.683.748-1.15.137-.353.3-.882.344-1.857.048-1.055.058-1.37.058-4.041v-.08c0-2.597-.01-2.917-.058-3.96-.045-.976-.207-1.505-.344-1.858a3.097 3.097 0 00-.748-1.15 3.098 3.098 0 00-1.15-.748c-.353-.137-.882-.3-1.857-.344-1.023-.047-1.351-.058-3.807-.058zM12 6.865a5.135 5.135 0 110 10.27 5.135 5.135 0 010-10.27zm0 1.802a3.333 3.333 0 100 6.666 3.333 3.333 0 000-6.666zm5.338-3.205a1.2 1.2 0 110 2.4 1.2 1.2 0 010-2.4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
								</svg>
								<span class="font-medium group-hover:underline">@firstlayerdigital</span>
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Development Process Section -->
			<div class="relative mb-12 sm:mb-16 md:mb-20">
				<div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-12 md:mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-4xl 2xl:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4">Our Development Process</h2>
					<p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-lg lg:text-xl 2xl:text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed px-2">
						From initial concept to a high-performance launch, here is how we build your digital presence.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="relative bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/20 p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 overflow-hidden">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50/30 via-transparent to-blue-50/20 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl -z-10"></div>
					
					<!-- Timeline container -->
					<div class="relative">
						<!-- Continuous progress line connecting all steps (desktop only) -->
						<!-- Positioned at center of w-20 icon (2.5rem = 40px) minus half line width (0.125rem = 2px) -->
						<!-- Line starts from center of first icon and ends at center of last icon -->
						<div class="hidden md:block absolute left-[2.375rem] top-10 bottom-[2.5rem] w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-cyan-400 via-cyan-500 to-cyan-600"></div>
						
						<!-- Process Steps -->
						<div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 md:space-y-10 lg:space-y-12 relative">
							<!-- Step 1: Discovery & Strategy -->
							<div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
								<div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center relative md:mr-0">
									<div class="relative z-10 w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg">
										<svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
											<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
										</svg>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
									<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl 2xl:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3 md:mb-4">1. Discovery & Strategy</h3>
									<p class="text-slate-700 mb-3 sm:mb-4 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg">
										Before we write a single line of code, we focus on your business goals. We conduct a deep dive into your brand, target audience, and competitors to define the site's requirements.
									</p>
									<div class="space-y-2.5 sm:space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mt-3 sm:mt-4">
										<div class="bg-cyan-50/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 border border-cyan-200/40">
											<div class="flex items-start gap-2.5 sm:gap-3">
												<div class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 shadow-md mt-0.5">
													<svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 sm:w-4 sm:h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
														<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
													</svg>
												</div>
												<div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
													<div class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base mb-0.5 sm:mb-1">Deliverable</div>
													<div class="text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">A project roadmap and technical requirements document.</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="bg-blue-50/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 border border-blue-200/40">
											<div class="flex items-start gap-2.5 sm:gap-3">
												<div class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 shadow-md mt-0.5">
													<svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 sm:w-4 sm:h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
														<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
													</svg>
												</div>
												<div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
													<div class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base mb-0.5 sm:mb-1">The Goal</div>
													<div class="text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">Ensuring the final product solves a real business problem.</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

							<!-- Step 2: Architecture & Design -->
							<div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
								<div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center relative md:mr-0">
									<div class="relative z-10 w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg">
										<svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
											<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"></path>
										</svg>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
									<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl 2xl:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3 md:mb-4">2. Architecture & Design</h3>
									<p class="text-slate-700 mb-3 sm:mb-4 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg">
										We map out the user journey. This begins with a sitemap and wireframes to define the structure, followed by high-fidelity UI designs. We focus on creating an intuitive experience that guides visitors toward your calls to action.
									</p>
									<div class="space-y-2.5 sm:space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mt-3 sm:mt-4">
										<div class="bg-cyan-50/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 border border-cyan-200/40">
											<div class="flex items-start gap-2.5 sm:gap-3">
												<div class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 shadow-md mt-0.5">
													<svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 sm:w-4 sm:h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
														<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
													</svg>
												</div>
												<div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
													<div class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base mb-0.5 sm:mb-1">Deliverable</div>
													<div class="text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">Interactive prototypes and visual design mockups.</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="bg-blue-50/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 border border-blue-200/40">
											<div class="flex items-start gap-2.5 sm:gap-3">
												<div class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 shadow-md mt-0.5">
													<svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 sm:w-4 sm:h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
														<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
													</svg>
												</div>
												<div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
													<div class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base mb-0.5 sm:mb-1">The Goal</div>
													<div class="text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">A beautiful, user-centric design that reflects your brand identity.</div>
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

							<!-- Step 3: Agile Development -->
							<div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
								<div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center relative md:mr-0">
									<div class="relative z-10 w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg">
										<svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
											<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
										</svg>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
									<h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl 2xl:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3 md:mb-4">3. Agile Development</h3>
									<p class="text-slate-700 mb-3 sm:mb-4 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg">
										This is where the vision comes to life. Using a modern tech stack, we build your site with clean, scalable code. We develop in "sprints," providing you with a staging link so you can see progress in real-time and provide feedback.
									</p>
									<div class="space-y-2.5 sm:space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mt-3 sm:mt-4">
										<div class="bg-cyan-50/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 border border-cyan-200/40">
											<div class="flex items-start gap-2.5 sm:gap-3">
